Titolo: Miss Spider's Sunny Patch Friends: Harvest Time Hop and Fly

Anno: 2006

Descrizione: Miss Spider's Sunny Patch Friends: Harvest Time Hop and Fly is a video game developed by Shin'en Multimedia based on the children's television show Miss Spider's Sunny Patch Friends. The game is designed for use on the Nintendo DS from publisher The Game Factory Aps. Players crawl into the world of Sunny Patch with Miss Spider, her husband Holley, and their gang of buggies as they harvest food and prepare for the coming of winter.